<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Whoa ho ho" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Whoa ho ho</orth> or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Whoa ho hoa,</orth> an exclamation to attract attention at a distance; used by Slender and the old shepherd in <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.187" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 187</bibl> &amp; <bibl n="shak. wt 3.3.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 3, 79</bibl>. cf. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 39</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>